        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_BODY_NAME": "The House",
        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "The House is an insane gambler who relies on his luck to overcome difficult situations, using two mysterious artifacts of fate: a 6-shot revolver called <style=cIsUtility>\"Roulette\"</style> and a seemingly cursed deck of cards. <i>Backported from pt-BR. Original mod by JavAngle. Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
