        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_BODY_MASTERY_SKIN_NAME": "Mastery",
        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_BODY_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..and so he left, playing tricks on fate once more.",
        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_BODY_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..and so he vanished, his luck finally having run out.",
        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_BODY_STANDARDSPREAD_NAME": "Standard Shot",
        "JAVANGLE_HOUSE_BODY_STANDARDSPREAD_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. Fire a random shot from your revolver.",
